1. *Doći* ću ti u petnaest minuta. (I will come to you in fifteen minutes.)

2. Njegova majka je *došla* da njega poseti. (His mother came to visit him.)

3. Oni će *doći* danas. (They will come today.)

4. Odlučio sam da *dođem* ranije. (I decided to come earlier.)

5. *Dolazak* je bio odložen za narednu nedelju. (The arrival was postponed for the next week.)

6. Ona je *došla* kasno. (She came late.)

7. Njegovi roditelji su *došli* da ga vide. (His parents came to see him.)

8. Ona je *došla* ranije nego što je planirala. (She came earlier than she had planned.)